Show No Mercy as Art the Clown in Terrifier: The ARTcade Game, Available Now on PlayStation 5!

Step into the chaos of this 2D beat ’em up set in the Terrifier universe and unleash pure mayhem as Art the Clown. Slice through hordes of enemies, destroy film sets trying to cash in on Art’s image, and leave a trail of carnage behind you.

- Featuring an original main theme by Cody Carpenter
- Local co-op with up to 4 players
- A brutal arsenal of weapons
- Multiple stages, branching paths, boss battles, and six game modes
- A retro-fueled chiptune soundtrack

Prepare for a terrifyingly good time on PlayStation 5.


Wreak havoc in Terrifier: The ARTcade Game, available now digitally on PlayStation 5 and coming in a physical edition on December 19th!
